  <brief_title>Determination of Risk Factors of Ventricular Arrhythmias (VAs) After Implantation of Continuous Flow Left Ventricular Assist Device With Continuous Flow Left Ventricular Assist Device (CF-LVAD)</brief_title>
  <acronym>ASSIST-ICD</acronym>
  <official_title>Interest of Implantable Cardioverter-defibrillator in Primary Prevention in Patient With Continuous Flow Left Ventricular Assist Device (CF-LVAD)</official_title>
